Package com.sun.jna.platform.win32.COM

Interface IRunningObjectTable

All Superinterfaces:
IUnknown
All Known Implementing Classes:
RunningObjectTable, RunningObjectTable.ByReference
public interface IRunningObjectTable extends IUnknown
Manages access to the running object table (ROT), a globally accessible look-up table on each workstation.
